title: 95. Are You Built For It?
itunes:title: 95. Are You Built For It?
description: Society will give you every reason as to why you can't become what it is you want to become. On today's episode, Andy debunks society's false narrative that success is only for specific individuals and gives you the recipe for achieving your goals.
